snippet.title: It's here! 🎮  The official Gameplay trailer for "Dwelling" is finally out!
snippet.description:
Description:Get ready to face your fears with our spine-chilling horror game, "Dwelling." The official Gameplay trailer is here, and it's packed with eerie atmosphere, mysterious puzzles, and heart-pounding moments that will keep you on the edge of your seat. Dive into the haunting world of "Dwelling" and uncover the dark secrets that lie within.

🔍 Explore the eerie environments
🧩 Solve intricate puzzles
👻 Experience the ultimate horror adventure

Stay tuned for more updates, and don't miss out on the terrifying journey that awaits you.

Subscribe and Follow Us:

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kodextra/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kode_xtra
Thread: https://www.threads.net/@kode_xtra
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/kodextra-solutions-pvt-ltd/

Release Date: july 7, 2024
Mark your calendars and prepare for the fear!
